{"tid":885740,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"「玉兔」撲港 凌晨掛八號波","createTime":"2018-11-01T14:30:29.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-01T14:38:02.000Z","uid":37380,"like":0,"dislike":35,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"ca8600a8a5dc8fedf959425375643c68d94f1af7","tid":885740,"uid":37380,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-01T14:30:29.000Z","msg":"　【本報訊】颱風「玉兔」今晨直撲本港，天文台於凌晨零點卅分懸掛八號風球，預料今日清晨，「玉兔」會最接近香港，約在香港西南一百五十公里掠過，屆時本港風力會增強至烈風甚至暴風程度，而且會有暴雨，天文台呼籲市民應採取各種防風措施，並遠離海邊，以免發生危險。<br />\n<br />\n　由於「玉兔」來勢𣳈𣳈，預料今日上午在廣東沿岸登陸前後，其風圈半徑會為本港帶來極惡劣天氣，預料海、陸空交通服務亦會受到影響，市民今早外出或上班前，應留意電台、電視台的天氣報告及各項通知。如要乘飛機遠行的旅客，出發前亦應該致電有關航空公司查詢航班情況。機場管理局亦會在有必要時成立緊急監控中心，在機場內設立十二個櫃位為旅客提供航班資料，減少上次颱風襲港時出現的混亂。<br />\n<br />\n　「玉兔」迫近前夕，本港天氣昨晚仍未算惡劣，入夜後風勢雖然逐漸增強，但沒有落雨，市面上的商業活動基本維持正常，但街上的行人比平時稀疏，當局亦出動人手在市區做各種防風措施，包括綁緊大樹及搬走或綑好垃圾桶等。臨海的尖沙咀碼頭及尖東一帶海邊，有不少市民流連觀浪，海面上的浪比平日大，已露出「白頭浪」。<br />\n<br />\n　受到「玉兔」影響，葵涌貨櫃碼頭昨晚十一時已停止交收，而民政事務總署亦已開放各區共十七個臨時庇護站，供有需要的市民入住。詳情可致電熱線二八三五一四七三查詢，該熱線二十四小時運作。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://paper.wenweipo.com/2001/07/25/HK0107250094.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fpaper.wenweipo.com%2F2001%2F07%2F25%2FHK0107250094.htm&d=rhwCuyOkgID7OebO1yMOFsVakpCEQgWe3bOYm8oES40%3D&h=1291477e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://paper.wenweipo.com/2001/07/25/HK0107250094.htm</a>"},{"pid":"88dbd9167542862f13d0dd42b9f20d79b2ff8928","tid":885740,"uid":78666,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-01T14:31:19.000Z","msg":"Show Blocked User - 比d爭扎我"},{"pid":"246d31d2a900f745f69796c2457abb4ed1e35c37","tid":885740,"uid":95221,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-01T14:31:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/999.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e3ce05edffcfea9366d5048aa16db440b5447c71","tid":885740,"uid":37380,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"246d31d2a900f745f69796c2457abb4ed1e35c37","tid":885740,"uid":95221,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-01T14:31:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/999.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-01T14:32:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d2c1bd5438574e24d2012cb423753d15d6135d1b","tid":885740,"uid":45232,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-01T14:32:21.000Z","msg":"建議以後打過八號波既風都要除名"},{"pid":"3fba021f6542eb8c7e6e0ab4c5f6deb715fa8319","tid":885740,"uid":43072,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-01T14:32:46.000Z","msg":"仲未玩厭？"},{"pid":"189e90e2c6aa314c35173689329a931f33c83a1e","tid":885740,"uid":169708,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-01T14:33:26.000Z","msg":"又係6點前落波"},{"pid":"6fe7cc1461d0acc900fc17314419e0689a5e6f7d","tid":885740,"uid":37380,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3fba021f6542eb8c7e6e0ab4c5f6deb715fa8319","tid":885740,"uid":43072,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-01T14:32:46.000Z","msg":"仲未玩厭？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-01T14:34:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4d2d25a0bb6df8734d77d67d813ff2e7976712ee","tid":885740,"uid":194012,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-01T14:35:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b55e6b6a9bb1fbe24a4a5e2a277a4449e43a1b87","tid":885740,"uid":183180,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-01T14:37:13.000Z","msg":"2001年<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7baff0f82445d2cc9ee541beada4c45023c60269","tid":885740,"uid":37380,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score"